{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And afterwards, we laid there struggling with our own conscience.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, about-- in the morning, when the dawn was breaking, we said to him, Hamek, go run.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Run out.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Run away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, there was, there was, there were means.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you jumped off the barbed wire, it was not electrified barbed wire that was on the top of the thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could run away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, and run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says-- we said, we don't care.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he says, no I can't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He says, I have no right to, you know, to endanger your life for my own safety.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was taken out-- it was the group of 12 other people-- taken to the killing grounds.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he did not die-- --The way the others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He refused to undress, and he just walked away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they shot him as he walked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When they brought the clothes back to the camp, his clothes were the only one had blood stains on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "To us, he was always the hero.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The things that he taught us, that he said to us, were the things that, that, we used to repeat in our-- among ourselves, the things that gave us strength.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was one of the brave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In our, in our minds, in our perception, he was one of the brave people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The-- as I told you, the administration of the camp was by, by the internal Jewish forces and by outside forces.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The Germans, whenever the gestapo from outside-- whenever the Germans suffered a, a, a, a defeat on the Russian front, whenever they got drunk, they would come to the camp and take the people out and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the camp, but take them outside and shoot them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
